{
    "description_long": "This object consists of four distinct grave markers, each with unique shapes and weathered appearances. The markers include two headstones with rounded and ornate tops, and two crosses\u2014one simple and one mounted on a rectangular base. The surfaces are predominantly gray stone, with patches of brownish discoloration suggesting age and exposure to the elements. The markers are thin in profile, as seen from the side views, and lack any visible inscriptions or detailed engravings. These grave markers are typical of a small urban cemetery or memorial site, providing a somber and respectful presence.",
